# ── Twilio Masked Calling ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get these from https://console.twilio.com
# 1. Sign up → get Account SID + Auth Token from dashboard
# 2. Buy an Indian virtual number (search +91 numbers, ~$1/month)
# 3. Make sure your BACKEND_URL is publicly accessible (use ngrok for local dev)
# TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=ACxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
# TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=your_auth_token_here
# TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER=+91XXXXXXXXXX
